  "original_title": "\u0b86\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1\u0bb2\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb8\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf  \u0bae\u0bc2\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb0 \u0bb5\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc0\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0bae\u0bcb\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 - \u0bae\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcb\u0ba4\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b87\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0b9a\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Ambulance collides with three three-wheelers - Drunken driver arrested",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Yesterday evening (22.07.2022) an ambulance belonging to Pokavantlawa Regional Hospital collided with three three-wheelers in Attan Alutgama area under Attan Police Division and three people were seriously injured and admitted to Dikoya Aadar Hospital.",
        "The said ambulance belonging to Pokavantlawa District Hospital, which was going from Aton area towards Bogavantlawa, initially collided with two tricycles which were going from Dikoya area towards Aton city and then collided with another tricycle parked there for about 100 meters and crashed into the entrance of the house near the road.",
        "Due to this accident, the house area was damaged and the three three wheelers were also damaged.",
        "It is reported that the driver of the ambulance was under the influence of alcohol and the local people caught him and handed him over to the police.",
        "A 60-year-old woman, a man and a 17-year-old youth were injured in the Kunitha accident.",
        "According to hospital sources, the injured woman suffered a fracture in her stomach, shoulder and a 17-year-old boy's arm.",
        "Aton Police arrested the ambulance driver who was under the influence of alcohol and are conducting further investigations related to the accident."
      ],
